What an honor it is to work with such talented people. 

I had the chance to meet and work with Sara who uses glass to design some of the most beautiful pieces of glass accessories, Gabi did the most stunning makeup, directed and trusted me to take photos of these incredible pieces designed by Sara, and Maeve who modeled and helped make the vision come together. 

Using my @hasselblad 500cm with the Hasselblad 150mm lens provided by @kehcamera 📸

From Sara:

These ethereal pieces which draw inspiration from the ocean and alluring mythology of sirens, echo the captivating essence of these mythical beings. Like sirens, glass embodies otherworldly captivation and magnetic energy, its ability to bend light and reflect its environment infusing each piece with a sense of wonder and allure. 

My ultimate aspiration is for those who wear my glass pieces to exude an air of boldness and confidence. Each piece a statement to individuality, inspiring those who wear them to embrace their uniqueness. As the pieces themselves are birthed in fire, it carries an innate power and resilience that can reminds us of our own strength. 

To wear glass is to embrace the potent fusion of artistry and elemental forces. A symbol for the connection to the very essence of existence.
